        "text": "@NowIsAllUHav @soigomaa There is no way you could know that. The door you did pick has a 1/3 chance of winning. The door you did not pick can have any chance of winning from 0% to 100%. There is no way to tell in the version of the problem Marilyn was asked.\n\nFor example, here's how it can be 0%:\n\nMonty",
